Package: blblm
Type: Package
Title: Fitting Linear Models by Applying Bag of Little Bootstrap
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Randy", family = "Lai", role = "aut"), person(given = "Xiaoxuan", family = "Hu", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "xiahu@ucdavis.edu"))
Description: This package performs the bag of little bootstrap (blb) on lm and glm function. In other words, it is a blb version of lm and glm which improves the accuracy and the efficiency of assessing the quality of estimators. 
